OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and bright start
OL,6,Fto the morning. Increasing cloud will
OL,7,Fsoon spread north followed by showery
OL,8,Frain from mid-morning. The day will be
OL,9,Fbreezy but warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe evening will continue
OL,12,Fcloudy with showery rain. This will
OL,13,Fbegin to clear from late evening with
OL,14,Fclear spells increasing later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,17,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Scattered
OL,18,Fshowers will build from mid-morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
